speak;;This is the first real map of the game.|It first tells important information to the player|One:If Senya or Schuri lose all their HP, they will return in the next chapter|But their opinion of you will drop as a punishment.|Second: The actions and objectives you complete in the game will impact your relationships with your party.|And these relationships with your party will impact the story and endings.|Certain actions will increase or decrease your relationships.;;;hint
speak;;For this chapter, you must defend the two villages.
