speak;;The boss of the chapter is injured and will attempt to run away to his fort|While multiple enemies spawn as he runs away.|These enemies will attack and destroy the village if they step on it.|Losing a village will anger Schuri.;;;narration_top
speak;;The boss is a high ranking member of a bandit gang.|Senya wants him dead because if he gets away he'll continue causing trouble.
